item.title: Ireland Bound
item.description: I seem to only be good at keeping up with this thing whenever I go through a major life shift. Lots of things have changed: I’ve left my role at Fair, I’m more than halfway done with the OMSCS program, and I’ve upped and moved to Dublin, Ireland. Wait What? Ireland? Yes, Ireland! Why? A variety of reasons: I was born and raised in the suburbs of Los Angeles. I went to university in Los Angeles.
